_sText:
Ths is the final version of fy_source_funmap. I've improved upon the last version of this map by changing and getting rid of the some of the stuff which is not needed.

Change Log:

Took out fog

Improved Lighting using lightmaps and changing skybox

Map now supports 20 players instead of 16 in the last versions

Playclip was used on the edges to stop people from camping there. 

Optimized it some more

Nav file now included

End Log


This map was created by me, known as Rawrr, you can see some of the changes in the change log and I hope that I have improved this map enough so its even more fun, balanced and better looking. If there are any serious bugs or glitches that I've missed then please tell me straight away and I will be able to release an updated version of this map.
